==English==
===Noun===
#(''grammar'') A [[participle]] ending with the suffix ''-ing'' that indicates an ongoing action or state in the present, preceded by a form of the verb ''to [[be]]'' to make the [[progressive tense]]s of a verb, and also functioning as an adjective.

